Practical Tools and Platforms
• Microsoft Defender for Cloud: Offers AI-driven threat detection for cloud networks and integrates with other security tools for centralised monitoring​
https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/defender-for-cloud/ai-threat-protection.

• Fortinet’s Security Fabric: Uses AI for malware detection, anomaly identification, and proactive threat intelligence updates​
